original_title: Neil Finn, Paul Kelly Goin' Your Way
overview: Earlier in 2013, Two of Australasia's greatest singer songwriters Neil Finn and Paul Kelly, brought their iconic songs on a landmark 20+ date tour across Australia. Finn and Kelly shared the stage throughout as members of the one band, singing and playing together a selection from their rich and varied songbooks. Over 100,000 people attended the shows, which included 5 sold out nights at the Sydney Opera House.
title: Neil Finn, Paul Kelly Goin' Your Way
